Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:17.55,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕らは未来を変える力を　夢に見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:36.14,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ノイズの中　聞こえて来た君の泣き声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:47.16,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑っていた　僕の弱さを暴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:52.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君の行く道は　君にしか分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.78,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}違う空　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:07.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕等は未来へ向かう勇気を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:13.33,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}欲しがって過去に迷う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:27.91,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君が笑うほんとうの現在へ帰り付くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:17.55,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我們夢想著  改變未來的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:36.14,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}雜音中  傳來你的哭泣聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:47.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揭開我  歡笑之下的軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:52.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的前路  只有你能決定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.78,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追逐著  不同的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:07.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我們渴求著前往未來的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:13.33,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}卻為此在過去迷失了方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:27.91,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直至回到你所微笑著的此時此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:31.24,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}金色の午後は　ママレイドティーとビスケット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:37.84,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}散らかったトランプで　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:46.44,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}さぁ夢の続きを占いましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:54.92,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いくつのドア　開くのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:23:02.87,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…サガシモノ　何処ニアル？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.89,0:23:06.94,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけを見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:11.10,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけ追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:18.46,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気づけば　私は迷子で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:26.83,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}秘密の暗号　君だけに送ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.24,0:23:30.00,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}はやく見つけて　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:35.65,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「私はここだよ。」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:31.24,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}金色的午後  品嘗著柚子茶和餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:37.84,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}收起散落一地的紙牌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:46.44,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}來  占卜夢境的後續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:54.92,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}會打開多少扇大門呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:23:02.87,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…尋找的東西  究竟在何處？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.89,0:23:06.94,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只注視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:11.10,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只追逐著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:18.46,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這才發現我迷了路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:26.83,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只向你送去  秘密的暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.24,0:23:30.00,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}快點找到我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:35.65,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「我在這裡哦。」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.01,0:01:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪都沒有發現契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時出現數隻沒有契約者的靈體…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是異常現象哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:01:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然變成這種表情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快看  奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷貝尤…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首都在燃燒…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:27.10,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憐憫的讚歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再快點  基爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈體的大規模襲擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從未見過的可怕數量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼靈體會突然發動襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去招集鎮壓部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把潘多拉的所有戰力集中到雷貝尤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話  首都會被毀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撲克為什麼會出現在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備爆彈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝填
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準確瞄準眉心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巴司卡維爾做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是他們  也沒有能力做到這種地步哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是什麼原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯的意志在哀嚎著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯的意志？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼  但總有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲小姐是靠直覺感覺到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯意志的異狀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個原因  讓阿比斯的平衡崩潰了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不能再發呆了  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  基爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該感到光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我染血黑兔大人來送你上路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也加入戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨角獸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子…我的孩子還在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪…到底在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  已經沒事了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶你回媽媽身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子  我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去安全的地方避難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真是太謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記顧慮你的體力  隨意施展力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴  你都這麼虛弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是低級靈體  還是多得數不清
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎麼殺也殺不完
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘多拉本部到底在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是極限了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是期待著奧茲的力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得拿出真本事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘋狂帽商
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑  艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡可能遠離瘋狂帽商
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:09:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否定所有與阿比斯關聯的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓其消失的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的靈體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去找基爾他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯的異變還沒有結束哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家人似乎都去避難了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來火爐這邊  艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是討厭的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像阿比斯一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.46,0:12:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在孤獨和絕望支配的黑暗深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是孤獨一人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天又一天地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複著與靈體們無意義的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身心都變得像冰一樣寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  直到你這個僕人出現為止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯是個比死還要殘酷的無間地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯的平衡崩潰的原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是阿比斯的意志覺得寂寞了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像艾莉絲一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許她正在孤獨和絕望中哀號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是風而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是靈體來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴司卡維爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利奧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來幫我們的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是服從命令而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要結束阿比斯目前的異狀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要奧茲·貝薩流斯的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就交給我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但請不要忘記了  小少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再見面的時候  我們可能又是敵人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  沒子彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.27,0:14:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘多拉的增援部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你們都沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把潘多拉的靈體瞬間消滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再用一次瘋狂帽商  把那怪物…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼虛弱的身體再使用力量的話  你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.27,0:16:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲  體力恢復了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子我們是逃不過阿比斯的試煉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海藻頭  再解放一次染血黑兔的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是艾莉絲  也不一定能贏過那怪物的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦  這是我的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這排骨精
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要結束阿比斯的異狀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就需要奧茲·貝薩流斯的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.49,0:17:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  雖然你現在還感覺不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你…  只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有能解開所有謎團並獲得真相的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.13,0:17:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你擁有掌控阿比斯的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想救她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有那個力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此別過了  艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是最後一天陪你玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.02,0:18:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是記憶碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這隻靈體有我失去的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此別過了  艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是最後一天陪你玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  傑克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要離開我  永遠陪在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託  拜託了  傑克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.76,0:19:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的聲音傳到阿比斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.28,0:19:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓另一個我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌控阿比斯的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  一副無精打采的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候  我感到好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快被靈體殺掉的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣死掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我連自己是什麼樣的存在都還沒弄清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再也見不到艾莉絲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次從內心深處感覺到想要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是好事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會以自我犧牲為由  輕視自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只有感到害怕  人才會開始變得堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我撤回我之前的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前說過你是個令人毛骨悚然的小鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.57,0:21:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我的聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你的過去是場悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓你感到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.13,0:21:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都會全心全意地接受你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  你只不過是個僕人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.73,0:22:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不等呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲  你太狂妄了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}父親不在了……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.34,0:23:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}我到底算什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.67,0:23:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}為什麼我一定要被否定！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.34,0:23:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}很想見一見吧  小少爺？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.10,0:23:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}就是說……我是個滿是缺陷的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.52,0:24:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}你如果得不到別人的認同--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.65,0:24:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}就不能存在了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.86,0:24:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  朝向否定的彼岸